import SandCrawler from './sandcrawler.png'
import T16 from './T-16.jpg'
import X34 from './x-34.jpg'
import TIE_ln from './tie_ln.jpg'
import snowSpeeder from './snowspeeder.jpg'
import tie_bomber from './tie_bomber.jpg'
import at_at from './at_at.png'
import at_st from './at_st.png'
import twin_pod from './twin-pod.jpg'
import sailBarge from './sailbarge.png'

const PHOTO_VEHICLES: object[] =  [
    {'Sand Crawler': SandCrawler},
    {'T-16 skyhopper': T16},
    {'X-34 landspeeder': X34},
    {'TIE/LN starfighter': TIE_ln},
    {'Snowspeeder': snowSpeeder},
    {'TIE bomber': tie_bomber},
    {'AT-AT': at_at},
    {'AT-ST': at_st},
    {'Storm IV Twin-Pod cloud car': twin_pod},
    {'Sail barge': sailBarge}
]

export default PHOTO_VEHICLES
